function getQueryString(name) {
	var reg = new RegExp("(^|&)" + name + "=([^&]*)(&|$)", "i");
	var r = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);
	if (r != null) {
 return unescape(r[2]);
	}
	return null;
}

     function changeTab(current,n,classname,tabname){
    for(var i=1; i<=n;i++){
   $("#"+tabname+i).attr("class","");
    } 
    $("#"+tabname+current).attr("class",classname);

	<script src="http://www.scholat.com/scripts/cookieUtil.gzjs?_dc=4d9c355cc55" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script>
 var account = "lqlz";
 
 if (account == null || account == "") {

	var logincookie = CookieUtil.get("STOKEN");

	if (logincookie != null && logincookie != "") {

  if (checkdate(logincookie.split("/")[1])) {

	          var currentUrl = window.location.href;

	          CookieUtil.set("H_U", currentUrl, "/", "/", null, true);

	          window.location.href = './login.html';
	      } else {

	          CookieUtil.unset("STOKEN", "/", null);
	      }
	}
	
 }

 function checkdate(cookiedate) {

	    var date = new Date(),
	      timestamp, newDate;

	    timestamp = date.getTime();

	    newDate = new Date(timestamp - 7 * 24 * 3600 * 1000);

	    var cookie_Date = new Date(cookiedate);

	    if (cookie_Date.getTime() > newDate.getTime()) {

	      return true;
	    }

	    return false;

	  }
	</script>

var StrutsUtils = {};

// gets an object with validation errors from string returned by 
// the ajaxValidation interceptor
StrutsUtils.getValidationErrors = function(data) {
    if (typeof data === "object") {
        return data;
    }
    else {
        if (data.indexOf("/* {") === 0) {
            return eval("( " + data.substring(2, data.length - 2) + " )");
        } else {
            return null;
        }
    }
};

StrutsUtils.clearValidationErrors = function(form) {
    var firstNode = StrutsUtils.firstElement(form);
    var xhtml = firstNode.tagName.toLowerCase() === "table";

    if(xhtml) {
        clearErrorMessagesXHTML(form);
        clearErrorLabelsXHTML(form);
    } else {
        clearErrorMessagesCSS(form);
        clearErrorLabelsCSS(form);
    }

    //clear previous global error messages
	if(StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] && StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] !== null) {
		form.parentNode.removeChild(StrutsUtils.errorLists[form]);
		StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] = null;
	}

};

StrutsUtils.errorLists = [];

// shows validation errors using functions from xhtml/validation.js
// or css_xhtml/validation.js
StrutsUtils.showValidationErrors = function(form, errors) {
    StrutsUtils.clearValidationErrors(form, errors);

	if (errors.errors) {
		var l, errorList = document.createElement("ul");

		errorList.setAttribute("class", "errorMessage");
		errorList.setAttribute("className", "errorMessage"); // ie hack cause ie does not support setAttribute

		for ( l = 0; l < errors.errors.length; l++) {
			var item = document.createElement("li");
			var itemText = document.createTextNode(errors.errors[l]);
			item.appendChild(itemText);

			errorList.appendChild(item);
		}
		
		form.parentNode.insertBefore(errorList, form);
		StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] = errorList;
	}

  var i, fieldName, firstNode = StrutsUtils.firstElement(form);
  var xhtml = firstNode.tagName.toLowerCase() === "table";
  if(errors.fieldErrors) {
    for(fieldName in errors.fieldErrors) {
      if(errors.fieldErrors.hasOwnProperty(fieldName)) {
        for(i = 0; i < errors.fieldErrors[fieldName].length; i++) {
          if(xhtml) {
            addErrorXHTML(form.elements[fieldName], errors.fieldErrors[fieldName][i]);
          } else {
            addErrorCSS(form.elements[fieldName], errors.fieldErrors[fieldName][i]);
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
};

StrutsUtils.firstElement  = function(parentNode, tagName) {
  var node = parentNode.firstChild;
  while(node && node.nodeType !== 1){
    node = node.nextSibling;
  }
  if(tagName && node && node.tagName && node.tagName.toLowerCase() !== tagName.toLowerCase()) {
    node = StrutsUtils.nextElement(node, tagName);
  }
  return node;  
};

StrutsUtils.nextElement = function(node, tagName) {
  if(!node) { return null; }
  do {
    node = node.nextSibling;
  } while(node && node.nodeType !== 1);

  if(node && tagName && tagName.toLowerCase() !== node.tagName.toLowerCase()) {
    return StrutsUtils.nextElement(node, tagName);
  }
  return node;  
};

StrutsUtils.previousElement = function(node, tagName) {
  if(!node) { return null; }
  if(tagName) { tagName = tagName.toLowerCase(); }
  do {
    node = node.previousSibling;
  } while(node && node.nodeType !== 1);
  
  if(node && tagName && tagName.toLowerCase() !== node.tagName.toLowerCase()) {
    return StrutsUtils.previousElement(node, tagName);
  }
  return node;  
};

StrutsUtils.addOnLoad = function(func) {
  var oldonload = window.onload;
  if (typeof window.onload !== 'function') {
    window.onload = func;
  } else {
    window.onload = function() {
      oldonload();
      func();
    };
  }
};

StrutsUtils.addEventListener = function(element, name, observer, capture) {
  if (element.addEventListener) {
    element.addEventListener(name, observer, false);
  } else if (element.attachEvent) {
    element.attachEvent('on' + name, observer);
  }
};

	<script>
 var account = "lqlz";
 
 if (account == null || account == "") {

	var logincookie = CookieUtil.get("STOKEN");

	if (logincookie != null && logincookie != "") {

  if (checkdate(logincookie.split("/")[1])) {

	          var currentUrl = window.location.href;

	          CookieUtil.set("H_U", currentUrl, "/", "/", null, true);

	          window.location.href = './login.html';
	      } else {

	          CookieUtil.unset("STOKEN", "/", null);
	      }
	}
	
 }

 function checkdate(cookiedate) {

	    var date = new Date(),
	      timestamp, newDate;

	    timestamp = date.getTime();

	    newDate = new Date(timestamp - 7 * 24 * 3600 * 1000);

	    var cookie_Date = new Date(cookiedate);

	    if (cookie_Date.getTime() > newDate.getTime()) {

	      return true;
	    }

	    return false;

	  }
	</script>

 	<script type="text/javascript">
    var suffix=0; 
    var ispost=false;
    
 function addMore(objectID, name, inputType, attachmentSecurity)
 {
	var Flag = false;
	if($(".fontClass input[type='file']").length > 0){
 
 $(".fontClass input[type='file']").each(function(){
 	
 	if($(this).val()==null || $(this).val().length==0){
  Flag = true;
  return false;
 	}
 });
	}
	if(Flag){
 return;
	}
  var div = document.createElement("div"); 
  div.className='fontClass';
  div.style.marginLeft="32px";
	      var span = document.createElement("span");
  span.innerHTML = "&nbsp;\u6743\u9650:";//权限
  if("frompost"==attachmentSecurity)
  {
   ispost=true;
   attachmentSecurity= "newAttachmentsSecurity";
   span.style.display="none";
  }
	      var object = document.getElementById(objectID); 
	      var br = document.createElement("br");
  //var br2 = document.createElement("br");
  
  var input = document.createElement("input"); 
  var button = document.createElement("img");
  var security = document.createElement("input");	
  var title = document.createElement("input");	   
  var Sys = {};
	      var ua = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
	      var IE = !!window.ActiveXObject || "ActiveXObject" in window;
	      if (IE) {
	     	Sys.ie = (ua.match(/.+(?:rv|it|ra|ie)[\/: ]([\d.]+)/) || [0, '0'])[1];
	      } 
  if(document.uniqueID){ //IE
 	if(typeof(Sys.ie) == "undefined")
  Sys.ie = ua.match(/rv:([\d.]+)/)[1];
    if(Sys.ie==9){ // for ie 9
     var radio0 = document.createElement("input");
 	 var radio1 = document.createElement("input");
 	 var radio2 = document.createElement("input");
 	 radio0.setAttribute("name","_radio"+suffix);  
 	 radio1.setAttribute("name","_radio"+suffix);	
 	 radio2.setAttribute("name","_radio"+suffix);	
    }else if (Sys.ie==10 || Sys.ie==11 ){ // for ie 10 , 11
   	var radio0 = document.createElement("input");
  var radio1 = document.createElement("input");
  var radio2 = document.createElement("input");
  radio0.name="_radio"+suffix;
  radio1.name="_radio"+suffix;
  radio2.name="_radio"+suffix;
    }
    else{
    var radio0 = document.createElement("<input type='radio' name='"+"_radio"+suffix+"'>"); 
    var radio1 = document.createElement("<input type='radio' name='"+"_radio"+suffix+"'>");
    var radio2 = document.createElement("<input type='radio' name='"+"_radio"+suffix+"'>");
    } 
  }else{//not IE
 	var radio0 = document.createElement("input");
 	var radio1 = document.createElement("input");
 	var radio2 = document.createElement("input");
 	radio0.name="_radio"+suffix;
 	radio1.name="_radio"+suffix;
 	radio2.name="_radio"+suffix;
  }	
  
	
  
  var label0= document.createTextNode("");
  var label1= document.createTextNode("");
  var label2= document.createTextNode("");
  
  
  if(ispost)
  {
 	radio0.style.display="none";radio1.style.display="none";radio2.style.display="none";
  }else
  {
   label0= document.createTextNode("所有人");
   label1= document.createTextNode("好友");
   label2= document.createTextNode("自己");
  
  }
  
  input.type = inputType;
  input.name = name;
  title.type = "hidden";
  
  title.name = "attachmentTitle";
  
  input.style.height="22px";
  input.style.width="330px";
  //button.type = "button";
  //button.value = "删除";
  button.style.marginLeft = "60px";
  //button.style.float="right";
  button.style.cursor="pointer";
  button.src="images/action_delete.gif";
  security.type= "text";
 	  security.name= attachmentSecurity;
 	  security.style.display="none";
  
  radio0.type="radio";	
  radio0.value="0";
  radio0.style.marginLeft="20px";
  
  radio1.type="radio";	
  radio1.value="1";
  radio1.style.marginLeft="20px";
  
  radio2.type="radio";	
  radio2.value="2";
  radio2.style.marginLeft="20px";
  suffix++;
  
  button.onclick = function()
  {
 	object.removeChild(div);
    div.removeChild(br);
   //div.removeChild(br2);
   div.removeChild(input);

   div.removeChild(title);
 	
   	 
   
   
   
   div.removeChild(span);
   
   div.removeChild(radio0);
   div.removeChild(label0);
 	 
   div.removeChild(radio1);
   div.removeChild(label1);
 	 
   div.removeChild(radio2);
   div.removeChild(label2);
 	 
   div.removeChild(security);
   div.removeChild(button);
   suffix--;
  }	
  
  radio0.onclick =function()
  {
   security.value= "0";
  }
  
  radio1.onclick =function()
  {
   security.value= "1";
  }
  
  radio2.onclick =function()
  {
   security.value= "2";
  }
  object.appendChild(div);
  div.appendChild(br);
  //div.appendChild(br2);
 	
  div.appendChild(title);
  
  div.appendChild(input);	
  
 	
 	 
  div.appendChild(span);
  	
  div.appendChild(radio0);
  div.appendChild(label0);
 	
  div.appendChild(radio1);	
  div.appendChild(label1);
 	
  div.appendChild(radio2);	
  div.appendChild(label2);	
 	
 	object.appendChild(security);
 	radio0.checked="true";	
  
 	security.value="0";         
 	div.appendChild(button);
  var saveAttachment = document.getElementById("saveAttachment");
  saveAttachment.style.display = "block"; 
 	
 
	
	
//	$(".fontClass >input[type=file]").val();
	
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
  function validateForm_postMessageEditForm() {
    var getFieldValue = function(field) {
      var type = field.type ? field.type : field[0].type;
      if (type == 'select-one' || type == 'select-multiple') {
        return (field.selectedIndex == -1 ? "" : field.options[field.selectedIndex].value);
      } else if (type == 'checkbox' || type == 'radio') {
        if (!field.length) {
          field = [field];
        }
        for (var i = 0; i < field.length; i++) {
          if (field[i].checked) {
            return field[i].value;
          }
        }
        return "";
      }
      return field.value;
    }
    form = document.getElementById("postMessageEditForm");
    clearErrorMessages(form);
    clearErrorLabels(form);
    var errors = false;
    var continueValidation = true;
    return !errors;
  }
</script>

 <script type="text/javascript">
 
 var editor = UE.getEditor('container',{
  toolbars:[
       [ 'undo', 'redo', '|',
        'bold', 'italic', 'underline','|', 'insertorderedlist', 'insertunorderedlist', 'lineheight', '|',
         'justifyleft', 'justifycenter', 'justifyright', 'justifyjustify', '|',
         'insertimage', 'link', '|',
         'inserttable', 'deletetable'
       ]
     ]
 });
 setTimeout(function(){
	 var postId = $("#postMessageId").val();
	 if (postId==''){	//新增动态
  if (editor.execCommand('getlocaldata')){
	 editor.execCommand('drafts'); //读取草稿箱内容
  }
  var title = getCookie("title");	//读取标题
  if (title!=''&&title!="在这里输入您的动态标题"){
	 $("#postMessageTitle").html(title);	
	 $("#postMessageTitle").css({color:"#000"});
	 var mylen = getStrLength(title);
	 $("#wordCheck").html(Math.floor((maxlen*2 - mylen)/2));
  }
	 }
 }, 500);
 function saveTitle(){
	 var postId = $("#postMessageId").val();
	 if (postId==''){	//只有新增动态的情况下才保存标题
  var title = document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").value;
  setCookie("title", title, 1);
	 }
 }
 var maxlen= 50;  
 function getStrLength(str){
  var mylen = 0;
  var i = 0;
  for(;(i < str.length); ++i){
  if(str.charCodeAt(i) != 32){
   if(str.charCodeAt(i) > 0 && str.charCodeAt(i) < 128){
   ++mylen; 
   }else{
   mylen += 2; 
   }
  }
  }
  return mylen;
 }
 $(function(){
  isOutOfLimit = false;
  var tipMsg = $("#postMessageTitle").val();
  if(tipMsg.length<1){
  $("#postMessageTitle").html("在这里输入您的动态标题");
  $("#postMessageTitle").css({color:"#ccc"});
  }
  $("#postMessageTitle").click(function(){ 
  var tipMsg2 = $("#postMessageTitle").val();
  　　　if(tipMsg2=='在这里输入您的动态标题'){
   $("#postMessageTitle").css({color:"#000"});
   $("#wordCheck").html("50");
  }
  }); 
  $("#postMessageTitle").focus(function(){
  var tipMsg4 = $("#postMessageTitle").val();
  $("#postMessageTitle").css({color:"#000"});
  　if(tipMsg4=='在这里输入您的动态标题')
   {
   $("#postMessageTitle").html("");
   }
  }); 
  $("#postMessageTitle").blur(function(){  
  var tipMsg2 = $("#postMessageTitle").val();
  　　　　if(tipMsg2.length==0){
    $("#postMessageTitle").html("在这里输入您的动态标题");
    $("#postMessageTitle").css({color:"#ccc"});    
   $("#wordCheck").html("50");
  }
  }); 
  var titleString = $("#postMessageTitle").val();
  var mylen = getStrLength(titleString);
  if(titleString == "在这里输入您的动态标题"){
  $("#wordCheck").html("50");
  }else{
  $("#wordCheck").html(Math.floor((maxlen*2 - mylen)/2));
  }
  $("#postMessageTitle").keyup(function(){
  var tipMsg3 = $("#postMessageTitle").val();
  var mylen = getStrLength(tipMsg3);
  $("#wordCheck").html(Math.floor((maxlen*2 - mylen)/2));
  if($("#wordCheck").html() < 0){
   $("#postMessageTitle").css("border","1px solid rgb(250,125,60)");
  }else{
   $("#postMessageTitle").css("border","1px solid gray");
  }
  });
  
  $.ajax({
  url: "checkLimitCondition.html",
  type: "post",
  success: function(data){
   if(data == "OutOfLimit"){
   isOutOfLimit = true;
   }
  },
  error: function(){
  // console.log("error");
  }
  })
 }); 
 var clickCount = 0;
  function teamworkListByUsername(){
  if(clickCount==1){
   clickCount=0;
   $("#teamList").hide();
   return;
  }else{
   clickCount = 1;
   if($("#teamList").html!=""){
   $("#teamList").show();
   }
  }
  $.ajax({
   contentType:"application/json;charset=utf-8",
   type:"post",
   url:"showteamworkListByUsername.html",
   timeout:100000,
   dataType:"json",
   cache:false,
   success:function(data){
   var html = "<ul style='margin: 5px 0 0 5px;'>";
   for(var i=0;i<data.length;i++){
    html = html + "<li style='line-height: normal;margin: 0;'><div style='float:left;padding-top:5px;'>"+
      "<input type='checkbox' value='"+data[i].id+"' name='checkbox'/></div><div style='float:left;padding-left: 5px;margin-top:5px;position: relative;'>"+data[i].name+
      "</div><div style='float:left;margin-left:15px;padding-top:5px;'><input type='radio' name='security"+data[i].id+"' value='0' checked='checked'/>公开可见<input type='radio' value='1' name='security"+data[i].id+"'/>成员可见</div><div style='clear:left;'></div></li>"
   }
   html = html + "</ul>";
   $("#teamList").html(html);
     },
   error:function(){
     $("#teamList").html("&nbsp;&nbsp;加载失败，请稍后再试！");
   }
  });
  }
  var clickCount2 = 0;
  function showCourseList(){
  if(clickCount2==1){
   clickCount2=0;
   $("#courseList").hide();
   return;
  }else{
   clickCount2 = 1;
   if($("#courseList").html!=""){
   $("#courseList").show();
   }
  }
  $.ajax({
   contentType:"application/json;charset=utf-8",
   type:"post",
   url:"showCourseList.html",
   timeout:100000,
   dataType:"json",
   cache:false,
   success:function(data){
   var html = "<ul style='margin: 5px 0 0 5px;'>";
   for(var i=0;i<data.length;i++){
    html = html + "<li style='line-height: normal;margin: 0;'><div style='float:left;padding-top:5px;'>"+
      "<input type='checkbox' value='"+data[i].id+"' name='checkbox2'/></div><div style='float:left;padding-left: 5px;margin-top:5px;position: relative;'>"+data[i].title+
      "</div><div style='clear:left;'></div></li>"
   }
   html = html + "</ul>";
   $("#courseList").html(html);
     },
   error:function(){
     $("#courseList").html("&nbsp;&nbsp;加载失败，请稍后再试！");
   }
  });
  }
  function dealWithPush(){
  var tipMsg = $.trim($("#postMessageTitle").val());
  if(tipMsg.length>500){
   goTop();
   blinkit();
   return false;
  }
  if(tipMsg.length<1||'在这里输入您的动态标题'==tipMsg){
   goTop();
   blinkit();
   return false;
  }
  if($("#wordCheck").html() < 0){
   
   $("#postMessageTitle").css("border","1px solid rgb(250,125,60)");
   goTop();
   blinkit();
   return false;
  }
  var checkbox = $("input[name=checkbox]:checked");
  if(checkbox.length>0){
   $("#pushToMyTeams").val("pushToMyTeams");
   var teamworkIds='';
   for(var i=0;i<checkbox.length;i++){
   var security = $("input[name='security"+checkbox[i].value+"']:checked").val();
   teamworkIds = checkbox[i].value+";"+security+ "," + teamworkIds;
   }
   $("#teamworkIds").val(teamworkIds);
  }
  var checkbox2 = $("input[name=checkbox2]:checked");
  if(checkbox2.length>0){
   $("#pushToCourse").val("pushToCourse");
   var courseIds=new Array();
   for(var i=0;i<checkbox2.length;i++){
   courseIds[i] = checkbox2[i].value;
   }
   $("#courseIds").val(courseIds);
  }
  if(isOutOfLimit){
   alert("您今天编辑的动态数量已经超出限制");
   return false;
  }
  }
  function deletePostMessage(id){
  var ret = window.confirm('您确定删除？');
  if(ret){
   location="removePostMessage.html?id="+id;
  }
  delCookie('title');
  delDrafts();	//删除后清空编辑器草稿箱
  }
  function blinkit()
  {
  intrvl=0;
  for(nTimes=0;nTimes<2;nTimes++)
  {
   intrvl += 200;
   setTimeout("refresh1()",intrvl);
   intrvl += 200;
   setTimeout("refresh2()",intrvl);
   }
  }
  function refresh1()
  {
  document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").style.opacity=0.8;
  document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").style.backgroundColor="#ea5858";
  }
  function refresh2()
  {
  document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").style.opacity=1;
  document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").style.backgroundColor="white";
  }
  var befst=0;
  function goTop(acceleration, time) {
   var docEle=document.documentElement;
   var aftst= docEle.scrollTop==0?document.body.scrollTop:docEle.scrollTop;
   if(befst<aftst && befst!=0)
   { 
   befst=0;
   aftst=0;
   return;
   }
   acceleration = acceleration || 0.1;
   time = time || 8;
   var x1 = 0;
   var y1 = 0;
   var x2 = 0;
   var y2 = 0;
   var x3 = 0;
   var y3 = 0;
   if (docEle) {
   x1 = docEle.scrollLeft || 0;
   y1 = docEle.scrollTop || 0;
   }
   if (document.body) {
   x2 = document.body.scrollLeft || 0;
   y2 = document.body.scrollTop || 0;
   }
   var x3 = window.scrollX || 0;
   var y3 = window.scrollY || 0;
   var x = Math.max(x1, Math.max(x2, x3));
   var y = Math.max(y1, Math.max(y2, y3));
   var speed = 1 + acceleration;
   window.scrollTo(Math.floor(x / speed), Math.floor(y / speed));
   if(x > 0 || y > 0) {
   var invokeFunction = "goTop(" + acceleration + ", " + time + ")";
   befst = docEle.scrollTop==0?document.body.scrollTop:docEle.scrollTop;
   window.setTimeout(invokeFunction, time);
   }
  }
  
   function delSpace(){
    document.getElementById("submitBtn").style.visibility="hidden";
  	setInterval("showBtn()",3000);
  	document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").value = document.getElementById("postMessageTitle").value.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
  	delCookie('title'); 
  	delDrafts(); //点击保存按钮后同时清除编辑器草稿箱内容
   }
   function showBtn()
   {
  	document.getElementById("submitBtn").style.visibility="visible";
   }
   function delDrafts(){	//清空编辑器草稿箱内容
  	localStorage.clear();
   }
   //设置cookie
   function setCookie(c_name, c_value, expire){
     var exdate = new Date();
     exdate.setDate(exdate.getDate()+expire);
     document.cookie=c_name+"="+escape(c_value)+((expire==null)?"":";expires="+exdate.toGMTString());
   }
   //获取cookie
   function getCookie(c_name){
     if (document.cookie.length>0){
       c_start = document.cookie.indexOf(c_name+"=");
       if (c_start!=-1){
      	c_start = c_start + c_name.length + 1;
      	c_end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", c_start);
      	if (c_end==-1)
        	c_end = document.cookie.length;
      	return unescape(document.cookie.substring(c_start, c_end)); 
       }
     }
     return "";
   }
   function delCookie(name)
   {
  	var exp = new Date();
  	exp.setTime(exp.getTime()-1);
  	var c_value=getCookie(name);
  	if(c_value!=null)
   document.cookie=name+"="+c_value+";expires="+exp.toGMTString();
   }
   function doReset(){	//重置
    $("#postMessageTitle").html("");
    editor.setContent("");
 $("#wordCheck").html(50); 
    delCookie("title");
    delDrafts();
   }
	</script>

<script>
window.onscroll=function()
{
 var docEle=document.documentElement;
 var st = docEle.scrollTop==0?document.body.scrollTop:docEle.scrollTop;
 var toTop = $("#toTop");
 if(st<520)
 {
  toTop.css("visibility", "hidden");
 }
 else
 {
  toTop.css("visibility", "visible");
 }
}
	</script>

function clearErrorMessages(form) {
	// clear out any rows with an "errorFor" attribute
	var divs = form.getElementsByTagName("div");
    var paragraphsToDelete = new Array();

    for(var i = 0; i < divs.length; i++) {
        var p = divs[i];
        if (p.getAttribute("errorFor")) {
            paragraphsToDelete.push(p);
        }
    }

    // now delete the paragraphsToDelete
    for (var i = 0; i < paragraphsToDelete.length; i++) {
        var r = paragraphsToDelete[i];
        var parent = r.parentNode;
        parent.removeChild(r);
    }
}

function clearErrorLabels(form) {
    // set all labels back to the normal class
    var labels = form.getElementsByTagName("label");
    for (var i = 0; i < labels.length; i++) {
        var label = labels[i];
        if (label) {
            if (label.className.indexOf("error") > -1) {
                label.className = label.className.substring(0, label.className.indexOf("error"));
            }
        }
    }

}

function addError(e, errorText) {
    try {
        var ctrlDiv = e.parentNode; // wwctrl_ div or span
        var enclosingDiv = ctrlDiv.parentNode; // wwgrp_ div

        /*alert(ctrlDiv.nodeName);
		if (!ctrlDiv || (ctrlDiv.nodeName != "DIV" && ctrlDiv.nodeName != "SPAN") || !enclosingDiv || enclosingDiv.nodeName != "DIV") {
			alert("do not validate:" + e.id);
			return;
		}*/
		
        var label = enclosingDiv.getElementsByTagName("label")[0];
		if (label) {
		    label.className += " error";
	    }
	    
	    var input = enclosingDiv.getElementsByTagName("input")[0];
	    if (input) {
	        input.className += " error";
	    }

		var firstDiv = enclosingDiv.getElementsByTagName("div")[0]; // either wwctrl_ or wwlbl_
		if (!firstDiv) {
			firstDiv = enclosingDiv.getElementsByTagName("span")[0];
		}
        var error = document.createTextNode(errorText);
        var errorDiv = document.createElement("div");
        
        errorDiv.className = "errorMessage";
        errorDiv.setAttribute("errorFor", e.id);;
        errorDiv.appendChild(error);
        firstDiv.appendChild(errorDiv);
    } catch (e) {
        alert(e);
    }
}

     function changeTab(current,n,classname,tabname){
    for(var i=1; i<=n;i++){
   $("#"+tabname+i).attr("class","");
    } 
    $("#"+tabname+current).attr("class",classname);

 function GetRequest() {
	var url = location.search; 
	var theRequest = new Object();
	if (url.indexOf("?") != -1) {
 var str = url.substr(1);
 strs = str.split("&");
 for ( var i = 0; i < strs.length; i++) {
 	theRequest[strs[i].split("=")[0]] = unescape(strs[i].split("=")[1]);
 }
	}
	return theRequest;
 }
 $( function() {
	var url = window.location.href;
	var tab;
	if (url.indexOf("tab=3") != -1) {
 tab = 3;
 $("#tabs_1").remove();
 $("#tabs_2").remove();
 $("#tabs_4").hide();
 $("#collectMessage").addClass("topClickBackground");
 $("#collectMessage").css("color","white");

 function deletePostMessage(id) {
	var ret = window.confirm('您确定删除该动态？');
	if (ret) {
 location = "removePostMessage.html?id=" + id;
	}
 }
 function deletePostMessageByAjax(id,elementId){
	var ret = window.confirm('您确定删除该动态？');
	if (ret) {
 if(elementId){
 	$.get("removePostMessage.html", {"id": id},
  function(req) {
 	$("#"+elementId).remove();
  }
 	);
 }else{
 	location = "removePostMessage.html?id=" + id;
 }
	}
 }
 function deleteReprintPostMessageByAjax(id,elementId){
	var ret = window.confirm('您确定取消转载该动态？');
	if (ret) {
 if(elementId){
 	$.get("removePostMessage.html", {"id": id},
  function(req) {
 	$("#"+elementId).remove();
  }
 	);
 }else{
 	location = "removePostMessage.html?id=" + id;
 }
	}
 }
 function deleteCollectPostMessageByAjax(id,elementId){
	var ret = window.confirm('您确定取消收藏该动态？');
	if (ret) {
 if(elementId){
 	$.get("postMessageCancelColl.html", {"id": id},
  function(req) {
 	$("#"+elementId).remove();
  }
 	);
 }else{
 	location = "postMessageCancelColl.html?id=" + id;
 }
	}
 }

	<script>
 var account = "lqlz";
 
 if (account == null || account == "") {

	var logincookie = CookieUtil.get("STOKEN");

	if (logincookie != null && logincookie != "") {

  if (checkdate(logincookie.split("/")[1])) {

	          var currentUrl = window.location.href;

	          CookieUtil.set("H_U", currentUrl, "/", "/", null, true);

	          window.location.href = './login.html';
	      } else {

	          CookieUtil.unset("STOKEN", "/", null);
	      }
	}
	
 }

 function checkdate(cookiedate) {

	    var date = new Date(),
	      timestamp, newDate;

	    timestamp = date.getTime();

	    newDate = new Date(timestamp - 7 * 24 * 3600 * 1000);

	    var cookie_Date = new Date(cookiedate);

	    if (cookie_Date.getTime() > newDate.getTime()) {

	      return true;
	    }

	    return false;

	  }
	</script>

	window.document.onkeydown = function doconkeydown() {
 if ((event.keyCode == 8)) {
 	if (window.event.srcElement.tagName.toUpperCase() != "INPUT" && window.event.srcElement.tagName.toUpperCase() != "TEXTAREA" && window.event.srcElement.tagName.toUpperCase() != "TEXT") {
  event.keyCode = 0;
  event.returnValue = false;
 	}
 }
	};
	startList = function () {
 if (document.all && document.getElementById) {
 	navRoot = document.getElementById("nav");
 	for (i = 0; i < navRoot.childNodes.length; i++) {
  node = navRoot.childNodes[i];
  if (node.nodeName == "LI") {
 	node.onmouseover = function () {
  this.className += "over";
 	};
 	node.onmouseout = function () {
  this.className = this.className.replace("over", "");
 	};
  }
 	}
 }
	};
	window.onload = startList;
	navList = function () {

function getQueryString(name) {
	var reg = new RegExp("(^|&)" + name + "=([^&]*)(&|$)", "i");
	var r = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);
	if (r != null) {
 return unescape(r[2]);
	}
	return null;
}
var src = getQueryString("source");
var sp = document.getElementById("sp_err");
if (getQueryString("error") == "true") {
	sp.innerHTML = "\u7528\u6237\u5bc6\u7801\u9519\u8bef";
	sp.style.display = "";
} else {
	if (getQueryString("error") == "idnull") {
 sp.innerHTML = "\u8be5\u5e10\u6237\u4e0d\u5b58\u5728";
 sp.style.display = "";
	} else {
 if (getQueryString("error") == "msg") {
	sp.innerHTML = "\u767b\u5f55\u540e\u7ee7\u7eed\u64cd\u4f5c";
	sp.style.display = "";
 } else {
	if (getQueryString("error") == "iddel") {
 sp.innerHTML = "\u8fdd\u89c4\u7528\u6237\uff0c\u5df2\u88ab\u6ce8\u9500";
 sp.style.display = "";
	} else {
 sp.style.display = "none";
 document.getElementById("sp_err").innerHTML = "&nbsp;";
	}
 }
	}
}
document.getElementById("j_username").focus();
function validateForm(form) {
	var session_value = "A496C677B0AC2670C19DE8FC2B759D4B.tomcat1";
	var psw = document.getElementById("j_password_ext").value;
	var key1 = session_value;
	var key2 = "userc";
	var key3 = "pfir";
	var enResult = strEnc(psw, key1, key2, key3);
	document.getElementById("j_passdec").value = enResult;
	return true;
}
